The Nigeria Centre for Disease Control (NCDC) has announced five new case of Coronavirus  (Covid-19). The NCDC disclosed this on its Twitter handle on Sunday night. It tweeted, “Five new cases of #COVID19 have been reported as follows: 2 in Lagos
2 in Kwara
1 in Katsina As at 09:10 pm 12th April there are 323 confirmed cases of #COVID19 reported in Nigeria. 85 have been discharged with 10 deaths.”  